data.description: Large 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with river view located just 20 minutes south of Florence in the small historic town of Gardiner. This large home has lots of charm and needs some interior updating. Nice customs features through out. Living room with fireplace, large kitchen with pantry & laundry room. Formal dining room with French doors to large deck out back. Lots of room for the whole family! Roof is less than 10yrs old. Corner lot with fruit trees, kiwi vine and lots of parking. Bring your tools and your beach toys. Dunes, Lakes, Trails, Rivers and Ocean are all close by. Plenty of room for everyone! Call for appointment and come take a look. Nice sunsets too!
